text: Michael J. Marino (June 11, 1930 – March 6, 2011) was an American politician who served in the New Jersey General Assembly from the 32nd Legislative District from 1974 to 1976. ==References== Category:1930 births Category:2011 deaths Category:Members of the New Jersey General Assembly Category:New Jersey Democrats Category:Politicians from Jersey City, New Jersey
